{"type":null,"faqId":19355,"title":"通话声音很小或有杂音","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>请在信号较好的环境下通话。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>手持模式下通话时，请适当调整握姿。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>将耳朵对准听筒的位置，可有效提高通话音量。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请注意不要用手指或其他物体遮挡住麦克风（通常在手机底部）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>手持模式下通话时，请注意声源距离麦克风 </span><span class=\"s2\">10cm</span><span> 以内。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>耳机模式下通话时声音很小或有杂音，请使用华为标配耳机进行通话，非标配耳机可能会出现不兼容的情况。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>通话过程中按音量上键可以提高通话音量。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>请尽量在噪音干扰小的环境中进行通话。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>若问题依然存在，请重启手机或备份重要数据后恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若重启手机或恢复出厂设置后通话仍然有问题，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>华为会定期在官网发布最新软件版本，以优化软件性能，请您及时升级软件，以体验更好的手机性能。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2496","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608224000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":94,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}